modName: Taae - Hybrid Female Orc Dark Elf
summary: An Orc hybrid save game blending Orc and Dark Elf Races
descriptionHtml:
An Orc hybrid save game blending Orcish and Dark elf races, Starts in Riverwood after I retrieved the golden claw and dragonstone.

I used the Player.setrace command to avoid changes to stats, then edited in Showracemenu and changed back. This way I could use certain features (Hair, eyes, skin color) that the Orcs don\'t have access to. If you feel the character needs editing just follow the example below, changing the features in showracemenu, but be aware that some features will change, such as the shape of the face.
Ie: Player.setrace darkelfrace > Showracemenu > Player.setrace orcrace


Mods Character uses: (Not sure if character height makes a difference, included just in case)
Better Females by Bella Version 3(http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812)
Less Make up Version 2(http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812)
Increased character height(http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3265)
High_Quality_Eyes-1_20(http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=498)
author: VazolRondeln
